## §2. 5-axis cross-contribution

- **Q (QUANTUM)**: covalent docking score (Glide CovDock, ICM Cov, Schrödinger CovalentDock); warhead Cys reactivity DFT calculation (B3LYP/6-31G*); transition-state energy for Michael addition; KRAS G12C switch-II pocket VQE binding energy; reversible covalent equilibrium k_on/k_off prediction; warhead intrinsic reactivity (GSH half-life) quantum-mechanical prediction; residence time τ = 1/k_off vs irreversible bond formation kinetics.
- **W (WEAVE)**: warhead-conjugate scaffold (Michael acceptor + scaffold linker); fragment-based covalent library design; reversible warhead chemistry (cyanoacrylamide, nitrile, α-ketoamide); SuFEx click chemistry assembly.
- **V (VIROCAPSID)**: minimal direct fit (covalent = small molecule paradigm); but capsid surface Cys conjugation (AAV bioconjugate engineering) niche overlap.
- **RB (RIBOZYME / RNA)**: covalent RNA modification — m6A writers (METTL3/14) and erasers (FTO, ALKBH5) covalent inhibitor paradigm; RNA-Cys-warhead covalent crosslink; covalent RNA aptamer.
- **NB (NANOBOT)**: covalent nano-conjugate (ADC linker chemistry — maleimide/Cys, NHS ester/Lys); brentuximab vedotin / T-DM1 / T-DXd payload conjugation; covalent PROTAC nano-delivery; warhead-decorated nanoparticle surface chemistry.

