## §4. Phase α–ε — hxq-covalent-krasg12d-001 candidate

- **Phase α (target select)**: KRAS G12D — most common KRAS mutation (~30% pancreatic, ~15% colorectal); harder than G12C (no Cys for direct covalent; G12D = aspartate, no nucleophile); beyond Mirati MRTX1133 (non-covalent G12D, Phase 1).
- **Phase β (warhead strategy)**: trans-covalent paradigm — engage neighboring Lys (K16 / K117) via sulfonyl fluoride (SuFEx) or aryl fluorosulfate; or trap switch-II via Cys185/Cys118 distal covalent; reversible covalent (α-ketoamide) for tunable residence.
- **Phase γ (Q-validation)**: DFT B3LYP/6-31G* warhead reactivity ranking; covalent docking + MD 100ns; transition-state energy <15 kcal/mol; selectivity vs HRAS/NRAS Cys.
- **Phase δ (W-axis library)**: 384-member SuFEx fragment library; activity-based protein profiling (ABPP) Cys/Lys reactivity map; cellular target engagement CETSA.
- **Phase ε (clinical hand-off)**: hxq-covalent-krasg12d-001 → KRAS G12D pancreatic cancer 1L combo with chemotherapy or immune-checkpoint; competing with MRTX1133 + RMC-9805.

## §5. raw#10 honest C3 — covalent paradigm renaissance

covalent inhibitor 의 paradigm 은 가장 오래된 약물 paradigm 중 하나 — aspirin (1899) COX1/2 Ser530 acetylation, penicillin (1942) PBP Ser, omeprazole (1989) H+/K+ ATPase Cys813 — irreversible binding 이 안전하지 않다는 두려움 ("hapten formation, idiosyncratic toxicity, off-target") 으로 1990–2000 년대 medicinal chemistry 에서 회피. 2010 년대 renaissance 시작 — Bradner/Gray "rational covalent" paradigm + ibrutinib 2013 BTK Cys481 first-in-class 으로 selectivity 를 통한 covalent 부활. 2015 osimertinib EGFR T790M Cys797 → 3rd-gen TKI. 2021 sotorasib KRAS G12C Cys12 — "undruggable target" 30년 myth 깨짐 (Shokat 2013 Nature paper "small molecules to a previously undruggable" → 8년 만에 FDA). 2024 revumenib menin covalent → leukemia 새 paradigm. Cys-targeting 강점: (a) selectivity — 단백질당 Cys 평균 6개, surface-exposed reactive Cys 는 ~280 개로 한정 (Cravatt ABPP 데이터), (b) residence time 무한대 (irreversible) → low-frequency dosing, (c) low Ki 보다 high k_inact 으로 efficacy 확보. 약점: (a) off-target reactive Cys labeling (proteomics 으로 측정), (b) hapten formation → drug-induced liver injury (DILI) idiosyncratic, (c) glutathione (GSH) conjugation으로 systemic clearance, (d) immunogenicity (covalent adduct = neoantigen), (e) resistance via Cys→Ser mutation (ibrutinib C481S 임상 기록). 한국 K-pharma covalent 진입 가능성: 유한양행 leclaza/lazertinib (Yuhan EGFR 3rd-gen covalent 한국 first FDA 2024), 한미약품 olmutinib (covalent EGFR, 한국 자체 개발 history), Bridge Biotherapeutics BBT-176 (4th-gen EGFR covalent, C797S resistance 극복), Daewoong covalent platform — 한국 covalent track record 있음. 양자-VQE fit: covalent docking 은 transition-state energy + bond-formation thermodynamics 을 quantum chemistry 로 계산해야 정확 (classical force field 한계) — DFT B3LYP/6-31G* 이 standard 이지만 VQE/QPE 로 nearer-future 정밀 가능; Cys reactivity (pKa, nucleophilicity, σ*) DFT calc 은 이미 routine; KRAS G12C switch-II pocket geometry 는 induced fit 이라 quantum precision 필요. reversible-covalent paradigm emergence: cyanoacrylamide (Taunton lab), nitrile (Pfizer), α-ketoamide (nirmatrelvir Paxlovid 2021) — k_off tunable 으로 irreversible 의 toxicity risk 회피하면서 residence time 확보; 이는 covalent 의 미래 mainstream 방향. covalent fragment screening (ABPP, MS-based, intact-protein MS) 은 fragment-based drug discovery (FBDD) 의 covalent 확장으로 Vividion (Bayer 인수), Revolution Medicines, Frontier Medicines 등 platform 회사 뒷받침. covalent-PROTAC overlap (DCAF16 covalent recruit, KEAP1 covalent) 으로 platform_molecular_glue 와 cross-cut.

